{"id": "143279762a73e3e05963b3184b40378b4a8e1c24059e16e484db01a143fdd654", "item_id": "18fabf4082:0", "text": "To allow RenderMan to control your geometry settings, these can be found in the RenderMan tab inside the"}
{"id": "c891df73080a1f0bead1c02a57f84f1e1242d4ac902c189c4f793618f0d5ac54", "item_id": "18fabf4082:1", "text": "RenderGeometrySettings"}
{"id": "3412b88ffdf62545b16c1292b28f7aa3d1902a1795c2b16b1974715186bd68d3", "item_id": "18fabf4082:2", "text": "LOP"}
{"id": "2e5f32e0d08ddc780910d9a31b36af4766dce19dbab003bfc92ce6cdc1b055e6", "item_id": "18fabf4082:3", "text": "(RfH needs to be installed)"}
{"id": "c7f937836f5d82d53bc507752075f87e25009ec11bc9fd4e282f0b645e47af7c", "item_id": "18fabf4082:4", "text": "Choose"}
{"id": "16aec665b4a8055a805a802c8c7d824825cdbdedbd88ed248326a5621a7c416c", "item_id": "18fabf4082:5", "text": "Set or Create"}
{"id": "05173d20d6ab25990802fb9686fd3c9c459fcca75c9d76ba15c4279ac8f48c0e", "item_id": "18fabf4082:7", "text": "Set if Exists"}
{"id": "fe1c0448bade71be54e758833d16e0981d17a2cac947d52b35469f06ba7e96c1", "item_id": "18fabf4082:8", "text": "to create or change an opinion on the geometry attribute or choose"}
{"id": "211d0bb8cf4f5b5202c2a9b7996e483898644aa24714b1e10edd80a54ba4b560", "item_id": "18fabf4082:9", "text": "Block"}
{"id": "5cb1d5b3fcf480740686410cadd2ca9fc61afcd0450143cfb1e4936fac5967f2", "item_id": "18fabf4082:10", "text": "to disable previous opinions on the attribute.   All available parameters are listed but none are set by default."}
{"id": "99bd94ada380007ca9388852bc101fbcd3102b3591763ab22f3faf5af559d457", "item_id": "18fabf4082:11", "text": "These are the same settings that can be found in the RenderMan spare parameter tab on object nodes."}
